parameters: Manager: Welcome, have you decided on your order?

Um, I was introduced by a person named Sonomori-
san...

Manager: From Sonomori-san...!? P-Please, have a
seat!

(I was half skeptical, but it looks like I'll be
treated to a feast♪ Lucky♪)

Manager: Here you go, this is the 'Homemade Milk
Coffee'.
Suuu... Mmm~ It smells so good... ♡ Let's dig in.

I really love the taste of the coffee and the
sweetness of the milk. I didn't know there was
such a good shop nearby.
.....You seem a bit down, don't you?

Manager: ...Actually, our shop started gaining
popularity after we created this menu...

Oh... But if the new menu became popular, then
that's a good thing, right...?

Manager: The problem is that we're having trouble
with the delivery of the milk, which is the core
of this product...

Could it be that you're using hard-to-find, high-
quality milk?

Manager: Um... I purchased it from a certain
person, Sonomori-san, but we only have 1200ml in
stock...

Manager: Furthermore, it seems that it's a special
milk that can only be squeezed from a cow that is
the only one in the world...
U-Um! C-Can I have a little taste of that milk?!

Manager: If just a little is fine, please go
ahead.

The liquid, more rich and sweet than milk... It
had a distinct taste. It was Ayako's breast milk,
which was extracted at Shilmania.

(W-Why are you here...! ...Ah!! Come to think of
it, that dandy voice...!)

(I remember...! That voice, it's the person who
extracted my breast milk...! Why didn't I realize
it sooner...!)

(M-More importantly...! If my breast milk is in
this coffee...!!)

Male Customer: What delicious milk coffee!! It
brings back memories of my childhood!

Female Customer: Refill! Refill!! More milk
coffee... No! I want a refill of milk, please!

(Ah... Ah... Ahh...! M-My breast milk... it's
being consumed by so many people like this...!)

(Hau...! ♡ M-My nipples are tingling and my
breasts are getting swollen...!)

(Ugh... I reacted to the fact that my breast milk
is being consumed...)

(Ugh... My breasts are being produced at an
incredible speed...! Haa... haa... they're already
getting swollen... I need to go home and express
them...)

Manager: Ah, um...! Earlier, you mentioned
something about 'mine', but could it be...!
Manager: Are you the one raising that dairy cow?!
N-N-Not a dairy cow...! \CE[31]... T-That's right.

Ayako Nagatsuki hesitated to deny being called a
dairy cow indirectly, but decided that it was
better to affirm it rather than revealing that it
was her own breast milk...

Manager: I have a favor to ask!! Please, could you
give me some milk?!

Manager: If we run out of stock and can't provide
the menu, this store will go bankrupt!!
Manager: Please...! Please sell me... your milk!!

W-Wait a minute! Y-Your voice is loud...! I-I
understand, so please be quiet...!

Manager: We have 500ml bottles prepared here! The
wholesale price is 5000 yen per bottle, and there
is no limit on the quantity, so please bring them
anytime!

(Ugh... It's embarrassing to think that someone
will drink it... What I'm doing is just like a
dairy cow...)

(But since I've already made a promise, if I'm
going to throw it away anyway, selling it might be
better...)

(But, where should I milk myself.... Rei-san is on
the first floor, and I can't really put it on my
desk, so where should I... \CE[31]ah....)

I have become able to milk myself once a day on
the second floor of my home.

The milk I've squeezed can be sold to the manager,
and depending on the amount sold, events may
occur. Let's squeeze it vigorously and sell it
off.
Female Customer: Is it okay if I'm alone?

What's the matter, Store Manager? Do you know
them?

Store Manager: D-Don't you know them, Nagatsuki-
san!? That person is not just a big eater, but
also a heavy drinker fighter, 'Whale Asami-san'!

Store Manager: The story goes that whenever she
visits a store, the inventory in the backroom gets
completely consumed and it results in amazing
sales!

Store Manager: But, the fact that such a big shot
came to a small coffee shop in the countryside...!

Female Customer: Excuse me, could I please have 30
cups of this special milk coffee?

Store Manager: As expected, the target is the milk
coffee...!!

Store Manager: Alright...! I'll accept that
challenge and...
Store Manager: Ouch!! My, my back pain...!

Store Manager: I-It's okay, just this much...!
A-As long as I don't move a single step, I'll be
fine...!

Store Manager: The coffee machine is here, so I
can somehow make the coffee... b-but... I might
not be able to move to the back yard...

Sigh, I guess there's no helping it. Store
Manager, please focus on making the coffee. I'll
help with bringing the necessary things if needed.
Store Manager: I-I'll take you up on your offer...

Store Manager: Then, please bring the milk from
the back as usual.

Female Customer: Phew~ Thank you for the delicious
meal♪

Female Customer: Especially the last five cups
were smooth, sweet, and incredibly delicious. The
aroma was also wonderful, it felt like there was
freshly squeezed milk in it.

Manager: I heard the news! Congratulations,
Nagatsuki-san!
Female Customer: By the way, how about over there?

Manager: This is the person who supplies milk to
our store. They are the owner of a very rare breed
of dairy cows.
W-Wait, Manager...! You don't have to say that...!

Female Customer: Please also convey my thanks to
the cow for the delicious milk!
The lewdness level has increased by 5...
Ayako earned 5000 yen as part-time job payment.

Manager: The last 5 cups that Nagatsuki-san made
were very well received. Did she do something
extra?

Eh!? Um... y-yes! I added a little bit of warmed
milk!

Manager: Amazing! Even though warming it too much
can diminish the flavor, being able to discern
that is impressive! You have excellent taste!

Manager: ...So, if it's alright with you, could I
ask for your help again today? My lower back is
still not in top condition...
Uhh... ♡♡ W-Well, if that's the case...

Manager: Thank you very much! Then, I'll leave the
milk to Nagatsuki-san! Please handle the way of
adding it.

if... if all the customers found out...)
